<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <!-- metadata -->
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <!-- page title -->
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <!-- common links -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/app.css">
    <!-- page specific links -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/help.css">
    <!-- favicon -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="./icons/favicon.ico">
    <!-- installable app -->
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="./icons/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="./icons/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="./icons/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="manifest" href="./manifest.webmanifest" crossorigin="use-credentials">
    <link rel="mask-icon" href="./icons/safari-pinned-tab.svg" color="#81c2c7">
    <meta name="msapplication-TileColor" content="#81c2c7">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#202124">
    <script src="./js/serviceWorker.js" async defer></script>
    <!-- common scripts -->
    <script src="./js/common.js" type="module"></script>
    <script src="./js/nav.js" type="module"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <script>0</script>
    {{! navigation bar }}
    {{> navbar}}
    {{! sidebar }}
    {{> sidebar}}
    {{! search screen + dimmer }}
    {{> search}}
    <!-- page content -->
    <main>
        <!-- help -->
        <section id="helpContainer" class="container">
            <h1>Help</h1>
            <p><b>MyStadiumNavigator</b> is designed as a Progressive Web Application, to bring stability to large venues near you.</p>
            <p>We provide seemless offline functionality, when network connections are poor. </p>
            <h2>Caching Data</h2>
            <p>With MyStadiumNavigator, you have the ability to cache application data, by clicking the dowload icons in the sidebar, to enable seemless navigation regardless of network connection.</p>
            <p>Cached pages will display a checkmark in the navigation bar.</p>
            <h2>User avatars</h2>
            <p>We have utilized <a href="https://robohash.org/" target="_blank">RoboHash</a> to provide you with fun profile avatars. Your initial avatar will be randomly generated. You can always generate a new one in your <a href="./profile">profile</a>!</p>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
